# NOTE: `deployments/` is intentionally NOT gitignored — it is persisted
# rocketh deploy state for REAL networks (e.g. `deployments/riseTestnet/`).
# Do not add a blanket `deployments` rule here.
#
# `deployments/localhost/` is the ONE exception: it is regenerated on every
# `bun run deploy:local` against a throwaway in-memory Hardhat node, so its
# addresses are ephemeral and not meaningful to commit. `TestLocalDeploy.test.ts`
# reads it fresh after a local deploy; it is not persisted deploy state.
deployments/localhost/

